sec.p:
As the last step in the manufacturing process, electrode metallization has been a major efficiency-limiting and cost-determining step of HJT solar cells. The power conversion efficiency (η) of solar cells is calculated according to Eq. 1:1η=PmaxPin=FF×Jsc×VocPin\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
